Actions:

    add department in models.company
    remove department from models.company
    list departments in models.company

    list employees in department

    list projects in department

    get person's age

    get number of years worked by an models.employee at the current job
    compute models.employee's salary
    get the manager of an models.employee's department

    manager can hire a person in his department
    manager can fire an models.employee from his department
    manager can start a models.project in his department
    manager can end a models.project in his department

    list models.project's tasks
    list models.project's team
    add task to models.project
    remove task from models.project
    add models.employee in models.project's team
    remove models.employee from models.project's team


